snippet.title: Auto Pirates: Captains Cup Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming soon to iOS and Android.

Auto Pirates is a competitive player vs world strategy game where you choose your crew, equip your ship and battle, earning plunder based on your global rank.

Earn plunder and collect trophies for your exploits on the seas and create the perfect pirate hideout for your crew.

Combine pirates from four fantasy factions with magical relics and a multitude of ships to optimize your strategy or create crazy hijinks. You can shoot, board, blast, burn, sink or push your opponents to get the upper hand and go for the top 1% prize.
